comments: Holiday (MIL) makes marginal contact to Sabonis' (SAC) body at the end of his drive that doesn't affect his SQBR.
Middleton (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Fox (SAC) and marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Sabonis (SAC) slightly extends his hand and he makes marginal contact to Matthews' (MIL) body that does not affect his ability to defend.
Lyles (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position during Antetokounmpo's (MIL) shot attempt near the rim. The contact that occurs is marginal.
Matthews (MIL) reaches around Mitchell (SAC) and makes marginal contact to his arm at the end of his drive.
Holiday (MIL) is the last player to touch the ball before going out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to SAC.
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Mitchell (SAC) commits a take foul on Portis (MIL).
